# Claude auth for agents inside the container.
# Generate with: claude setup-token   (bills to your Max subscription quota,
# NOT pay-per-use; valid 1 year; shares rate limits with interactive sessions).
# NEVER also set ANTHROPIC_API_KEY here — it takes precedence over this token
# and silently switches the fleet to metered API billing.
CLAUDE_CODE_OAUTH_TOKEN=

# Fine-grained GitHub PAT scoped to alexjba/status-desktop ONLY
# (Contents: RW, Pull requests: RW, Issues: RW). Never a full-scope token —
# the whole point of the sandbox is limiting blast radius.
GITHUB_TOKEN=
